edu.unm.health.biocomp.carlsbad

Class carlsbad_utils

  • Object
    • carlsbad_utils

  • public class carlsbad_utils
extends Object
    Static utility methods for CARLSBAD database system.
    Uses PostgreSQL JDBC driver (org.postgresql.Driver). For chemical cartrige gNova Chord DB.
    Issue: Cytoscape 2.8.1 fails to import string values containing unescaped < or > So, we HTM escape these fields.
    Issue: When searching by substance synonym (e.g. drug name "adderall"), it may be there are other stereoisomer substances (same compound, same smiles, different iso_smiles) which are not included.
    Issue: to add scaffold weighting, perhaps AtomCount(scaf)/AtomCount(mol). alpha-char-count is close enough (ignoring non-alpha chars in smiles).
    Author:
    Jeremy J Yang

      • Extract2XGMML

        public static HashMap<String,Integer> Extract2XGMML(DBCon dbcon,
                                                    File fout,
                                                    ArrayList<Integer> tids,
                                                    String sbs_id_query,
                                                    String sbs_idtype_query,
                                                    String qcpd,
                                                    String matchtype_qcpd,
                                                    Float minsim,
                                                    String cname,
                                                    boolean matchtype_cname_sub,
                                                    Integer mw_min,
                                                    Integer mw_max,
                                                    ArrayList<Integer> cids_query,
                                                    ArrayList<Integer> scafids_query,
                                                    ArrayList<Integer> mcesids_query,
                                                    Boolean neighbortargets,
                                                    String title,
                                                    Integer n_max_a,
                                                    Integer n_max_c,
                                                    ArrayList<String> sqls)
                                             throws Exception
        Given a set of targets and compound query criteria, extract subnet comprised of targets, compounds, scaffolds, mces, and activities. NOTE: XGMML attribute types: string,real,integer,boolean,list,map,complex TO DO: [x] target synonyms must be in lists, since multiple PDBs, Uniprots, etc may exist. [ ] adjustable limits on tids, cids or act_ids.
        Note that no HTML escape codes of the form &foo; are permitted in the XGMML file (e.g. by Cytoscape 2.8.2) and will result in a fatal error on import.
        Parameters:
        dbcon - database connection
        fout - XGMML output file
        tids - target IDs specified
        sbs_id_query - substance ID
        sbs_idtype_query - substance ID type
        qcpd - compound query SMILES/SMARTS
        matchtype_qcpd - compound query type (sim|exa|sub)
        minsim - similarity threshold
        cname - compound name
        matchtype_cname_sub - compound name query as substring
        mw_min - min molecular weight
        mw_max - max molecular weight
        cids_query - compound IDs specified
        scafids_query - scaffold IDs specified
        mcesids_query - MCES IDs specified
        neighbortargets - Should targets associated with subnet compounds also be included?
        title - title of subnet
        n_max_a - max number of activities
        n_max_c - max number of compounds
        sqls - return param: SQLs used
        Throws:
        Exception
